channel.title: Overthinking with Irrational Thoughts - Azure Onxyscore [Dark, Orchestral, Electronic]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/overthinking-with-irrational
Sometimes overthinking may cause one to be overly cautious of their actions, sometimes those thoughts can be irrational. Once those irrational thoughts affect the individual, it may destroy them from the inside, with new knowledge that they were wrong the whole time.
This track uses melodic samples which is present in the verses of the track.
